{"tid":360822,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[潛水、多圖] 菲律賓 PG島","createTime":"2017-08-15T15:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T08:15:19.000Z","uid":56020,"like":20,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb5a64091cf2fd7fe39739ba61fb168b666cd17","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"我早前去左菲律賓 Puerto Galera (PG島)潛水，玩左5日4夜，仲影左好多相。<br />\n潛左三日水，頭尾兩日就用黎搭車搭船。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPG島其實係馬尼拉南面一個島嘅一小部份，係一個渡假區，都算幾多野食，仲有幾間韓國餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由機場去PG島大約要3-4個鐘。潛水resort會有專車由機場接送到碼頭，大約兩至三個鐘。後再坐一個鐘船就到。通常第一日去到都係夜晚。<br />\n<br />\nPG島嘅潛點有三十幾個，大部份都係Sabang beach 附近，坐快艇十五分鐘之內就到，非常方便。<br />\n<br />\n潛點有深有淺，適合唔同level嘅diver。<br />\n聽講呢到一年四季都可以潛水。我之前四月去，水溫26-30C，算幾暖；而能見度通常都7m以上。<br />\n<br />\n咁PG島潛水有乜野睇呢？<br />\n除左大量珊瑚之外，仲有好多細魚同小動物。大魚同海龜都有，不過就比較少見。<br />\n<br />\n神象魚(Moorish idol)一地都係<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/224911_ad02eb844d092c6ed5232b84314f9270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F224911_ad02eb844d092c6ed5232b84314f9270.jpg&h=dbe88ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會見到一群群笛鯛(Indian snapper)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/225029_8aef9bc6c0a8fdcec6840d67abba92ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F225029_8aef9bc6c0a8fdcec6840d67abba92ba.jpg&h=174d463c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無數咁多條花鱸(anthias)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/225216_ae1a3a52c1c844c8cfd30b8d8c249cbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F225216_ae1a3a52c1c844c8cfd30b8d8c249cbf.jpg&h=410df860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連小丑魚都有好幾個品種，呢款叫做tomato clownfish<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/225610_e2dc1273c3aec6daf3aaee64f8ead03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F225610_e2dc1273c3aec6daf3aaee64f8ead03a.jpg&h=0bc56aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多好多好多種海蛞蝓(nudibranch, 呢款叫做<em>Chromodoris annae</em>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/225646_f3d5e2e0c8b5b4d499f06f9365a3d727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F225646_f3d5e2e0c8b5b4d499f06f9365a3d727.jpg&h=ae343a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且仲有偽裝蟹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/230803_5346f7e2134013ea56cf8a6bcda9f3a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F230803_5346f7e2134013ea56cf8a6bcda9f3a2.jpg&h=f5781948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左珊瑚區之外，PG潛水有兩樣野一定要玩，第一係潛沙地，第二係夜潛，不過我遲下再講。<br />\n<br />\n如果對野生動物有興趣，可以follow 我IG: gomenwl<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fedd104a620810e8f9706d3c2bf3018904aea70","tid":360822,"uid":66423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbda88c06a7f2ada6c2f62886e371219215419b5","tid":360822,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"唔玩埋anilao？"},{"pid":"30c315969abeb16c2fb45cdcc037b550d7a86e1e","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔玩埋anilao？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔夠時間，個時只係留係菲律賓5日<br />\n而且都未玩曬pg嘅潛點<br />\n<br />\n有機會我想去Anilao, 可以瘋狂加樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff408594377953bc3c41e5dbe4bb891520348ab0","tid":360822,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"總共用左幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706ee1c3503b20cf5e9305205334cfa61a5f9c8d","tid":360822,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有潛水牌? 用咩相機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce05d323daa87e1bf4db12732aed3c6390312e3f","tid":360822,"uid":105671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"其實夜潛有咩特別 係咪睇到多啲夜晚先出沒既生物？"},{"pid":"7c63aa057d832890c596de61bf1cd1d7dd5b2f1f","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總共用左幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部加埋$7xxx"},{"pid":"816a020756ab72f6733f02521590bbe43e0a1c0c","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有潛水牌? 用咩相機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有潛水牌<br />\n我用sony RX100V"},{"pid":"a3b1b0f01fb87888f1a79f1ab961c1ce7b7c8b31","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實夜潛有咩特別 係咪睇到多啲夜晚先出沒既生物？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n例如某d品種嘅魟魚(sting ray, 魔鬼魚親戚)，同叫做spanish dancer嘅海兔<br />\n<br />\n同埋會見到d魚停低係到訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bef18648f25a157ef236af3a34b3b571bd3320","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:14:30.000Z","msg":"珊瑚區固然多野睇，不過沙地都有好多特別野睇<br />\n<br />\n我個人推界兩個潛點 The Hall 同埋 Secret Bay(Dalaruan Bay)<br />\n<br />\n首先沙地有好易見到海馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/214805_8407922d0555cbc6e72ff6b91faa1096.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F214805_8407922d0555cbc6e72ff6b91faa1096.jpg&h=d9f899a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻海馬大左肚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/214855_369be21c9647f65c7293afb3b70f2c02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F214855_369be21c9647f65c7293afb3b70f2c02.jpg&h=d3da0bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子魚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/220411_17b9485b2795f917e047c2a5e8bc907a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F220411_17b9485b2795f917e047c2a5e8bc907a.jpg&h=0fd8ac35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/220458_35b96180f21b937a7ad5754d9d7df6c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F220458_35b96180f21b937a7ad5754d9d7df6c3.jpg&h=cbdf8c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會變色嘅墨魚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/220726_4788e2310ba6938138f847fb3e394dec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F220726_4788e2310ba6938138f847fb3e394dec.jpg&h=7b4dadc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/220813_20223cdf735a05f66596535621f30fc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F220813_20223cdf735a05f66596535621f30fc6.jpg&h=f5912b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/220843_f610201c385155594045ecbd2c5455f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F220843_f610201c385155594045ecbd2c5455f8.jpg&h=da123efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有螳螂蝦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/221038_5e5136c39bdf81deb935f2929012e7e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F221038_5e5136c39bdf81deb935f2929012e7e7.jpg&h=7146d609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d動物通常係珊瑚堆會比較少見，但係就容易係沙地見到<br />\n<br />\n但係留意，呢兩個dive site大約20m深，而且係平地，所以用氣會比平時快<br />\n所以要留意呼吸"},{"pid":"73a0e7a332b46f09b2fa18fbd24cac2f6efe4b64","tid":360822,"uid":105671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n例如某d品種嘅魟魚(sting ray, 魔鬼魚親戚)，同叫做spanish dancer嘅海兔<br />\n<br />\n同埋會見到d魚停低係到訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n停咗喺度 你游過果陣 佢地有冇嚇醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7471e74711938c6621e6132ab29b5ee1e477b0d7","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n例如某d品種嘅魟魚(sting ray, 魔鬼魚親戚)，同叫做spanish dancer嘅海兔<br />\n<br />\n同埋會見到d魚停低係到訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n停咗喺度 你游過果陣 佢地有冇嚇醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大部份都訓到豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc27dabe42b20c4fced903359efb077e77422a1","tid":360822,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有潛水牌? 用咩相機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有潛水牌<br />\n我用sony RX100V</blockquote><br />\n師兄我都想考潛水牌,你建唔建議係菲律賓考？係咪會平過第二到考？同埋如果菲律賓考牌係可行係菲律賓邊到考會好d?thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c055d530a49e0d45e80999a7778557ff999932a","tid":360822,"uid":98186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"32d452973c71af90fab044f3654a9cf12653a2b3","tid":360822,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有潛水牌? 用咩相機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有潛水牌<br />\n我用sony RX100V</blockquote><br />\n師兄我都想考潛水牌,你建唔建議係菲律賓考？係咪會平過第二到考？同埋如果菲律賓考牌係可行係菲律賓邊到考會好d?thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得係香港考好d，因為香港水域能見度差，所以係香港搞得掂，其它地方都無問題<br />\n<br />\n如果你想係菲律賓學， PG會係一個適合嘅地方，因為佢嘅深度同環境都適合新手<br />\n至於學潛水係唔係特別平我就唔清楚，但係菲律賓本身潛水係比較平<br />\n<br />\n但係有一點非常重要，有d外國教練教得好差，特別係收好平個d<br />\n所以如果真係要去菲律賓學又唔係香港潛水店搞嘅團，要特別留意口碑"},{"pid":"159e849b20a6a03f4db33ac0f6a9e3ad2bf7a020","tid":360822,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有潛水牌? 用咩相機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有潛水牌<br />\n我用sony RX100V</blockquote><br />\n師兄我都想考潛水牌,你建唔建議係菲律賓考？係咪會平過第二到考？同埋如果菲律賓考牌係可行係菲律賓邊到考會好d?thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc